Sum of array elements

Write a  program to find the sum of elements in an array.

Sample Input:

3
1
2
3

Sample Output:
6

Source Code:
import java.util.*;
public class Sumarray
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
        int a=sc.nextInt();
        int b[]=new int[a];
        int sum=0;
        for(int i=0;i<a;i++)
        {
        b[i]=sc.nextInt();
        }
        for(int i=0;i<a;i++)
        {
            sum=sum+b[i];
        }
          System.out.println(sum);
    }
    
        
}
